biospec_descr.textblock:
Biosampling is optional and includes:
- biosamples specifically collected for this research: blood samples (for DNA extraction and storage, peripheral white blood cells, and plasma); skin biopsy for isolation, culture and storage of fibroblasts; urine; saliva;
- biosamples collected in clinical routine, part of it being stored for research purposes: CSF, salivari accessory gland biopsies.
